Hey, guess what? He sent us a present!

rows.label: tlk41100122_03_msg0002

There was a letter in it, too.
You and my older brother solved that case
together, right?

rows.label: tlk41100122_03_msg0003

That's so, so cool! My older brother was a
huge star!
